$PROBLEM 031 SAEM
$INPUT ROW ID TIME EVID CMT AMT II ADDL DV MDV
$DATA ../NMsimData_xgxr032_noname.csv IGN=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 TRANS4
$PK LTVKA=THETA(1) LTVV2=THETA(2) LTVCL=THETA(3) LTVV3=THETA(4) LTVQ=THETA(5)
MU_1=LTVKA KA=EXP(MU_1+ETA(1)) MU_2=LTVV2 V2=EXP(MU_2+ETA(2)) MU_3=LTVCL CL=EXP(MU_3+ETA(3)) MU_4=LTVV3 V3=EXP(MU_4+ETA(4)) MU_5 = LTVQ Q =EXP(MU_5+ETA(5)) S2=V2
$ERROR IPRED=F IRES=DV-IPRED
IF (IPRED.GT.1) THEN W = SQRT(IPRED**2*SIGMA(1,1) + SIGMA(2,2)) ELSE W=1 ENDIF
IWRES=IRES/W Y=F+F*ERR(1)+ERR(2)

$OMEGA 0 FIX $OMEGA 0.173132 FIX $OMEGA 0.324497 FIX $OMEGA 0 FIX $OMEGA 0 FIX
$SIGMA 0.0809353 FIX $SIGMA 0 FIX
$SIMULATION ONLYSIM (360866430)
$TABLE ROW KA V2 V3 CL Q PRED IPRED Y NOPRINT FILE=xgxr032_noname.tab
